      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-int-ctr-001          .
           inspect   w-int-via-azi    tallying w-int-ctr-001
                                          for  trailing  spaces       .
           move      30                   to   w-int-via-azi-ndc      .
           subtract  w-int-ctr-001        from w-int-via-azi-ndc      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Localita' azienda                           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      rf-ada-loc-azi       to   w-int-loc-azi          .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Numero caratteri per localita' azienda      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-int-ctr-001          .
