      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Data bilancio                               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "PF"                 to   p-ope                  .
           move      "D"                  to   p-tip                  .
           move      p-lnr                to   p-lin                  .
      *
           if        rr-tip-stp           =    01
                     move  49             to   p-pos
